OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Details of public
OL,4,Cinquiry revealed
OL,6,FThe families of the victims of the
OL,7,FNottingham attacks attended Parliament
OL,8,Fas the government formally announced
OL,9,Fmore details of a judge-led inquiry,
OL,10,Fwith the Justice Secretary insisting
OL,11,Fit will be 'thorough' and 'unsparing'.
OL,13,FThe families watched from the public
OL,14,Fgallery of the House of Commons as MP
OL,15,FShabana Mahmood spoke about the full
OL,16,Fstatutory inquiry, which was first
OL,17,Fpromised by the PM earlier this year.
