OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Details of public
OL,4,Cinquiry revealed
OL,6,FShe said: "The Prime Minister promised
OL,7,Fwe would heed calls for a public
OL,8,Finquiry. I can today announce that a
OL,9,Ffull statutory inquiry will take
OL,10,Fplace. It will be chaired by Her
OL,11,FHonour Deborah Taylor and it will have
OL,12,Fthe power to compel witnesses.
OL,14,F"This inquiry must be thorough in its
OL,15,Fassessment of the facts and unsparing
OL,16,Fin its recommendations. That is the
OL,17,Fvery least that we owe to those who
OL,18,Fhave lost so much and fought so hard
OL,19,Ffor this moment.
