OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Details of public
OL,4,Cinquiry revealed
OL,6,FThe attacks took place on 13 June,
OL,7,F2023, when Valdo Calocane fatally
OL,8,Fstabbed university students Barnaby
OL,9,FWebber and Grace O'Malley Kumar as
OL,10,Fwell as school caretaker, Ian Coats.
OL,12,FThree other people were also seriously
OL,13,Finjured after Calocane drove a van
OL,14,Finto them.
OL,16,FSince the attacks, the families of the
OL,17,Fvictims have been fighting for justice
OL,18,Fand Keir Starmer confirmed earlier
OL,19,Fthis year that a judge-led public
OL,20,Finquiry into the attacks would take
OL,21,Fplace.
