OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Details of public
OL,4,Cinquiry revealed
OL,6,FThe families hope that the inquiry
OL,7,Fwill "uncover the truth" and explore
OL,8,Ffailings from multiple agencies to
OL,9,Fhold those responsible to account - as
OL,10,Fwell as introducing changes in laws
OL,11,Fand practice to ensure mistakes are
OL,12,Fnot repeated.
OL,14,FWho is the judge?
OL,16,FFormer senior circuit judge, Her
OL,17,FHonour Judge Deborah Taylor, has been
OL,18,Fselected by the Lord Chancellor to
OL,19,Fchair a full statutory inquiry into
OL,20,Fthe attacks.
