OL,6,FHH Deborah Taylor was a Senior Circuit
OL,7,FJudge, Resident Judge at Southwark
OL,8,FCrown Court and Recorder of
OL,9,FWestminster until her retirement from
OL,10,Fthe Judiciary in December 2022.
OL,12,FIn 2019 she jailed Julian Assange for
OL,13,Fbreaching his bail condition and in
OL,14,F2022 she jailed former tennis star
OL,15,FBoris Becker after he avoided paying
OL,16,Fhis debts.
