OL,6,FIn 2022 Taylor was Treasurer of Inner
OL,7,FTemple, where she advocated for
OL,8,Fgreater diversity at the Bar and she
OL,9,Fhas also chaired the Criminal Legal
OL,10,FAid Advisory Board (CLAAB) since July
OL,11,F2023.
OL,13,FThe Lord Chancellor confirmed HH
OL,14,FDeborah Taylor would undertake a
OL,15,Fthorough, independent assessment of
OL,16,Fthe attacks and the events leading up
OL,17,Fto them in order to provide
OL,18,Frecommendations to prevent similar
OL,19,Fincidents.
