OL,4,Cinquiry revealed
OL,6,FWhen will the inquiry take place and
OL,7,Fhow long will it take?
OL,9,FNow the chair has been appointed,
OL,10,Fpreliminary work can begin and the
OL,11,FMinistry of Justice says the final
OL,12,FTerms of Reference will be published
OL,13,Fas soon as possible. It says HH
OL,14,FDeborah Taylor has already engaged
OL,15,Fwith survivors and victims' families.
OL,17,FThe Prime Minister has committed that
OL,18,Fthe inquiry should release its report
OL,19,Fwithin two years.
OL,21,FWho will be called to give evidence?
