OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Details of public
OL,4,Cinquiry revealed
OL,6,FThe Justice Secretary said the inquiry
OL,7,Fwill have the power to "compel
OL,8,Fwitnesses" and it will examine all of
OL,9,Fthe agencies involved, including the
OL,10,Fpolice and the Crown Prosecution
OL,11,FService.
OL,13,FCalocane, who had been diagnosed with
OL,14,Fparanoid schizophrenia before the
OL,15,Fattacks, admitted three counts of
OL,16,Fmanslaughter on the grounds of
OL,17,Fdiminished responsibility and three
OL,18,Fcounts of attempted murder - and was
OL,19,Fsentenced to a hospital order in
OL,20,FJanuary 2024.
