OL,6,F"He is the product of a system that
OL,7,Fhas failed. Failed at every single
OL,8,Flevel. Countless opportunities to
OL,9,Fintervene and stop him were missed.
OL,10,FBarney, Grace and Ian have paid the
OL,11,Fultimate price for this shameful level
OL,12,Fof incompetence, and that must not be
OL,13,Fin vain.
