OL,6,FNeil Hudgell of Hudgell Solicitors,
OL,7,Fwho represents the families, said in a
OL,8,Fstatement: "Today is a watershed day
OL,9,Ffor the families of Barney, Grace and
OL,10,FIan, as this Public Inquiry is being
OL,11,Fheld only as a result of their
OL,12,Fdetermined pursuit of full
OL,13,Ftransparency and accountability for
OL,14,Fthe many, many failings of state
OL,15,Forganisations which have been
OL,16,Fidentified since June 2023.
