OL,6,F"Despite these many investigations
OL,7,Fhowever, true transparency and
OL,8,Faccountability has not yet been
OL,9,Fforthcoming. It is that which has made
OL,10,Fa Statutory Inquiry like this, which
OL,11,Fhas wide-ranging powers and is able to
OL,12,Fcompel people to give evidence and be
OL,13,Fquestioned under oath, essential.
OL,15,FIt added that the families have had
OL,16,Fthe opportunity to meet with the Chair
OL,17,Fand they are "confident that
OL,18,Ftransparency and accountability can
OL,19,Fnow be achieved".
